---
title: Beetroot Relish-Glazed Beef Meatballs with Chive Cauli-Potato Mash & Garden Salad
description: How many meatballs are too many? The answer is you can never have enough of these herb-infused beef meatballs covered in a velvety beetroot relish. A cauliflower and potato mash balances the whole dish out for you to enjoy until your appetite is content.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
